60 Williamstown Road Lanesborough, MA 01237 We're located right on Route 7 (Williamstown Road is Route 7) in Lanesborough, MA just north of Bailey Road. You'll see our sign down by the road. We share the driveway with our neighbor, so once you turn in, stay straight/left up the small hill and continue to our house (cinnamon colored with green trim) where you'll find a few parking spaces.